{
  "id": "adv_card_ktn_06_03",
  "title": "長瀬琴乃 3話 もう負けたくないから",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "liveseat",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――スリクス単独ライブ開演前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Before the start of IIIX's solo live",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "ここが、スリクスのライブ会場……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is the venue for IIIX's live…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.2333333055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "思ったより小さいな、と思っただろ？　同じことを\nファンが……そして本人達が一番感じてるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You thought it would be bigger‚ didn't you?\nThe fans thought the same‚ and so do the members themselves.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.1999999086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "liveseat",
      "startTime": 14.3833332578
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4じゃなくなり、所属事務所もあんなことに\nなって……。大変なのはもちろん分かってましたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They're no longer part of BIG4‚ and their agency is\nin that situation… I knew it would be tough‚ of course.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.6499999244,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "仕事一つ勝ち取るのも、ライブ会場を確保するのも\n大変な状況だよ。信用は地道に回復するしかないからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's tough trying to secure a job and a live venue in this situation.\nRebuilding trust is the only way forward.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.4666660666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "liveseat",
      "startTime": 30.7451690077
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "今のスリクスのモチベーションはなんなんでしょうか？\n這い上がるのは……凄く、大変ですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's driving IIIX's motivation right now?\nCrawling back up… must be incredibly difficult.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.6451690077,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6754.830992300001,
          "startTime": 41.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "liveseat",
      "startTime": 39.7118356744
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それはライブを観たら分かると思う\nお、始まるみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think you'll understand when you see their live performance.\nOh‚ it looks like it's starting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.6333322246,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3800.0000279000046,
          "startTime": 46.4333322525
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3800.0000279000046,
          "startTime": 46.4333322525
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "liveseat",
      "startTime": 46.1999989192
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "す、凄い……I-UNITYの頃より\nパフォーマンスに磨きがかかってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-UNITY days had a certain majesty to them‚ didn't they?\nBut now‚ I feel the determination to climb back up from here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.7370966474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "liveseat",
      "startTime": 54.3704299807
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスはもう終わりだ……なんて周囲の言葉を\n彼女達はまるで気にしてないんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Despite what people around them say‚\nlike \"IIIX is finished‚\" they don't seem to care.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.066665558,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "「次はサニーピースに必ず勝つ」と意気込んで\n今も成長を続けてるんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They're determined to beat Sunny Peace next\nand keep growing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.7333322246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "liveseat",
      "startTime": 68.2098623156
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "パフォーマンスを観れば\nそれが本気なんだってよく分かります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I watched their performance‚\nI could tell they were dead serious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.1431956489,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "liveseat",
      "startTime": 72.8098623156
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "I-UNITYで戦った時は、王者の貫禄のような\nものがあったと思うんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Back when we fought against I-UNITY‚\nthey had the air of champions‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.2765289823,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "liveseat",
      "startTime": 83.1765289823
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "今は、ここから這い上がるんだっていう凄みを感じます\nギラギラしてて……まるで猛獣みたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but now I sense their determination to climb from the bottom.\nThey're burning with intensity… like wild beasts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.1765289823,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（釘付けになってる。思うことは沢山あるだろうけど）\n（強烈な魅力がもやもやした想いを上回ってるんだな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I'm captivated. There must be a lot on their minds‚）\n（but their overwhelming charm surpasses any lingering doubts.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.7666625062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "liveseat",
      "startTime": 95.7824677188
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "這い上がるのは辛いとしか思えなかったんですけど……\nあんな風に力に変えることも出来るんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I used to think that climbing back up was just painful‚\nbut… I realize now that you can turn those pent-up emotions",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.722792767,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "liveseat",
      "startTime": 103.3824677188
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "「溜め込んだ気持ちを\n前に進むための燃料にしてしまえばいい」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "into fuel to move forward.\n\"Turn the stored-up emotions into fuel for moving forward.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.9509447904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "liveseat",
      "startTime": 108.4502797324
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんがこの間言っていた\n言葉の意味がよく分かりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's what you told me the other day‚ {user}-san.\nI understand the meaning of those words now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.9502797324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます、やる気がもっと出てきました\n本当に、今の私に必要なことが分かってるんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. I'm feeling even more motivated now.\nYou truly understand what I need at this moment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.6169463991,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "liveseat",
      "startTime": 122.3502782065
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "いつもは鈍感なのに、大事な時は鋭いんですよね\nそういうところに、きっと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're usually clueless‚ but you're sharp when it matters.\nI'm sure… that's your strength.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.5169448732,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "liveseat",
      "startTime": 130.2169652182
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　どうした？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? What's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.2169652182,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "……なんでもないです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Nothing",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.5361860472,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2930.4867230000013,
          "startTime": 135.4666727702
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 135.0666859308
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 135.0666859308
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスのライブ、凄く良かったです\nパフォーマンスもMCも参考になりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "IIIX's live was fantastic.\nI found their performance and MC helpful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.8666859308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（情熱に満ちた目だ……これなら安心だな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She has such passionate eyes… I can feel at ease with this.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.3361860472,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 149.3444401461
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "私は負けません\nスリクスにも、サニピにも、どんなライバルにだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won't lose.\nNot to IIIX‚ not to Sunny Peace‚ not to any rival.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.5444401461,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
